features: THE QUALITY IS SECOND TO NONE: Don't let the affordability fool you, this tooth brush set is super high quality. You’ll receive (25) premium disposable toothbrushes in a variety of colors; perfect for differentiating with others in your home. Use them once and toss or wash and reuse, the choice is yours.

MEDIUM/SOFT BRISTLES THAT GENTLY DEEP CLEAN: Each toothbrush is 7 inches long with ergonomic grips and medium/soft bristles. They're perfect for removing stains, plaque, and tartar without causing irritation to your gums

YOU WON’T HAVE TO CUT OR TEAR APART THE WRAPPER: All of our toothbrushes are individually wrapped and easy to open. They're perfect for donations, travel, camping, guests, gift shops, homeless shelters, care packages, dentist offices, and so much more.

THE COVERS MAKE THEM MORE HYGIENIC: No one wants to brush their teeth with a dirty toothbrush. Yuck! Have no fear. Each brush in our soft toothbrush set comes with a cover that protects the bristles from dirt and other junk.

MAKING YOU SMILE IS OUR #1 PRIORITY: Our goal is to have all of our customers grinning from ear to ear. If you have any questions about our products or your order, please let us know, we are happy to help!
body.description: Are you searching for a high quality, affordable pack of toothbrushes for your home, business, or to give away? Wouldn’t it be nice to buy a bulk pack of tooth brushes and have each one individually wrapped to maximize hygiene? If you answered YES to either question, then you’re going to love our Bulk Toothbrush Pack With Covers! When most people think of bulk packs of toothbrushes the idea of high quality doesn’t come jumping out. They’re mostly picturing cheap, flimsy toothbrushes that can only be used once. We wanted to change that. We think you can “have your cake and eat it too.” This 25-pack of travel toothbrushes is ultra-high-quality and affordable too. You can either use them one time and toss or long term (dentists recommend you change your toothbrush every 3-4 months). That’s how durable they are. They're also perfect for donations, travel, camping, guests, gift shops, homeless shelters, care packages, dentist offices, and so much more. Every toothbrush in this set comes individually wrapped in plastic to maximize cleanliness. The plastic is very easy to open too. You won’t have to rip or tear apart these wrappers. Product Features & Benefits: ✅ 25 multi-color premium toothbrushes ✅ Professional, durable design (7 inches) ✅ Made with medium/soft bristles ✅ Removes stains, plaque, and tartar ✅ Each toothbrush comes with a cover ✅ Individually wrapped in plastic for hygiene

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These are really nice!
reviews.reviewText: I got these for guests, and also to include as supplies for underprivileged people when assembling boxes to give out.Anyway, they’re individually wrapped, which is awesome, the cap to protect the bristles is already attached and the handles have that same ergonomic shape and color of a name brand toothbrush that my dentist hands out.I thought these were a GREAT deal and I’ve added them to my subscribe and save - the discount is nice, but keeping them in stock is awesome as well.
